<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbce96466-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c" identifier="/us/usc/t31/s507"><num value="507">§ 507.</num><heading> Office of Electronic Government</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Office of Electronic Government, established under <ref href="/us/usc/t44/s3602">section 3602 of title 44</ref>, is an office in the Office of Management and Budget.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbce96467-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/107/347/tI/s102/c/1">Pub. L. 107–347, title I, § 102(c)(1)</ref>, <date date="2002-12-17">Dec. 17, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/2910">116 Stat. 2910</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
