<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idbce96469-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idbce9646a-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective 120 days after <date date="2002-12-17">Dec. 17, 2002</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/107/347/s402/a/1">section 402(a)(1) of Pub. L. 107–347</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t44/s3601">section 3601 of Title 44</ref>, Public Printing and Documents.</p>
</note>
